'''瑪麗蓮·瓊斯·莫斯比'''（{{lang-en|Marilyn Jones Mosby}}，{{bd|1980年|1月22日|}}），是一位[[美國人|美國]][[律師|律師]]，現任[[美國|美國]][[馬里蘭州|馬里蘭州]][[巴爾的摩市|巴爾的摩市]][[州檢察官|州檢察官]]<ref name=NBCMosbyBio/>。

她因為在2015年5月1日，宣布正式[[起訴|起訴]]六名涉及[[弗雷迪·格雷之死|弗雷迪·格雷之死]]的警員{{link-en|謀殺罪 (美國法律)|Murder (United States law)|二級謀殺}}與過失殺人（Involuntary manslaughter）罪，而在全美國知名。

==早年生活==
莫斯比出生於[[波士顿|波士顿]]附近的{{link-en|多切斯特 (波士顿)|Dorchester, Boston|多切斯特}}，由[[祖母|祖母]]撫養長大。{{sfn|Adams|2013|p=A10}}她的父母都是擔任警察，且她的家族中有5人擔任警察。<ref name=NBCMosbyBio/>她曾於離家一小時車程的{{link-en|Dover-Sherborn High School|Dover-Sherborn High School}}求學，並參加了學生會兼校報主編{{sfn|Adams|2013|p=A10}}；對法律工作產生興趣，是因為她的17歲[[表哥|表哥]]，被另一個17歲少年誤認為{{link-en|非法毒品交易|Illegal drug trade|毒販}}，而遭到[[槍擊|槍擊]]身亡。<ref name=NBCMosbyBio/>

她曾獲得[[獎學金|獎學金]]，在[[阿拉巴馬州|阿拉巴馬州]][[塔斯基吉大学|塔斯基吉大学]]學習{{sfn|Adams|2013|p=A10}} ；並遇見了未來的[[丈夫|丈夫]]尼克·莫斯比（Nick Mosby），尼克現在是{{link-en|巴爾的摩市議會|Baltimore City Council}}的議員<ref name=NBCMosbyBio/> ；之後她在[[波士顿学院法学院|波士顿学院法学院]]，取得了[[法律博士|法律博士]]學位<ref name=NBCMosbyBio>{{cite news |title= Meet Marilyn Mosby, the Woman Overseeing the Freddie Gray Investigation |work= NBC News |first= Elizabeth |last= Chuck |date= April 30, 2015 |url= http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/baltimore-unrest/meet-marilyn-mosby-woman-overseeing-freddie-gray-investigation-n351046 |accessdate= 2015-05-03 |archive-date= 2021-03-09 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210309192421/https://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/baltimore-unrest/meet-marilyn-mosby-woman-overseeing-freddie-gray-investigation-n351046 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

==職業生涯==
2005年至2012年間，她擔任巴爾的摩市助理州檢察官<ref name= topprosecutor/>。2012年，她是[[利寶互助保險|利寶互助保險]]公司的律師<ref name= defeats>{{cite news |title= Mosby defeats Bernstein in Baltimore prosecutor's primary |work= The Daily Record |date= June 24, 2014 |url= http://thedailyrecord.com/2014/06/25/mosby-defeats-bernstein-in-baltimore-prosecutors-primary/ |accessdate= May 1, 2015 |archive-date= 2020-10-30 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201030174410/https://thedailyrecord.com/2014/06/25/mosby-defeats-bernstein-in-baltimore-prosecutors-primary/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>。

2013年，她宣布參選巴爾的摩市的州檢察官<ref name= topprosecutor>{{cite web |url= http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2013-06-24/news/bs-md-ci-marilyn-mosby-20130624_1_top-prosecutor-west-baltimore-bernstein |title= Marilyn Mosby seeks to become city's top prosecutor |work= The Baltimore Sun |first= Luke |last= Broadwater |date= June 24, 2013 |accessdate= May 1, 2015 |archive-date= 2015-05-03 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150503221537/http://articles.baltimoresun.com/2013-06-24/news/bs-md-ci-marilyn-mosby-20130624_1_top-prosecutor-west-baltimore-bernstein |dead-url= no }}</ref>。她在[[美國民主黨|民主黨]]的黨內初選中主打反對當時的擔任州檢察官的格雷格·伯恩斯坦（Gregg Bernstein）<ref name= topprosecutor/>，這使她在黨內初選中獲得了55％的選票<ref name= defeats/>，其後她在沒有[[反對黨|反對黨]]參選人的情況下參加大選<ref>{{cite news |title= Neverdon loses again as he strives for place on November ballot |first1= Kevin |last1= Rector |first2= Ian |last2= Duncan |work= The Baltimore Sun |date= September 9, 2014 |url= http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-neverdon-loses-appeal-20140909-story.html |accessdate= 2015-05-03 |archive-date= 2018-06-12 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20180612143007/http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/baltimore-city/bs-md-ci-neverdon-loses-appeal-20140909-story.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>，結果她以94％的選票擊敗了獨立參選人Russell A. Neverdon Sr.{{sfn|Alejandro|2014|p=A3}}<ref name= lawyer>{{cite news |title= Mosby is next Baltimore state's attorney |first= Ian |last= Duncan |work= The Baltimore Sun |date= November 4, 2014 |url= http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/politics/campaign-2014/bs-md-ci-city-races-20141104-story.html |accessdate= 2015-05-03 |archive-date= 2015-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20151208151854/http://www.baltimoresun.com/news/maryland/politics/campaign-2014/bs-md-ci-city-races-20141104-story.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。在此次選舉中，她是全美國最年輕的州檢察官候選人。<ref>{{cite news |title= New Baltimore State's Attorney Marilyn Mosby — youngest chief prosecutor in a major U.S. city — is set to take on the Freddie Gray case |first= Nancy |last= Dillon |work= New York Daily News |date= April 30, 2015 |url= http://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/freddie-gray-case-tough-task-new-state-attorney-article-1.2205884 |accessdate= 2015-05-03 |archive-date= 2020-12-08 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20201208153952/https://www.nydailynews.com/news/crime/freddie-gray-case-tough-task-new-state-attorney-article-1.2205884 |dead-url= no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |title= Who is Marilyn Mosby?: Prosecutor in Freddie Gray case has talked of need to 'repair' trust |first1= Dana |last1= Ford |first2= Ray |last2= Sanchez |publisher= [[CNN|CNN]] |date= May 1, 2015 |url= http://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/30/us/baltimore-freddie-gray-prosecutor/ |accessdate= 2015-05-03 |archive-date= 2021-01-25 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210125031904/https://edition.cnn.com/2015/04/30/us/baltimore-freddie-gray-prosecutor/ |dead-url= no }}</ref>

她在2015年1月8日宣誓就職<ref name= sworn>{{cite news |title= Marilyn Mosby sworn in as Baltimore City state's attorney: Mosby, 34, becomes youngest top prosecutor in U.S. |date= January 9, 2015 |work= [[WBAL-TV|WBAL-TV]] |location= Baltimore, Maryland |url= http://www.wbaltv.com/politics/marilyn-mosby-sworn-in-as-baltimore-city-states-attorney/30611736 |accessdate= 2015-05-03 |archive-date= 2016-04-05 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20160405081436/http://www.wbaltv.com/politics/marilyn-mosby-sworn-in-as-baltimore-city-states-attorney/30611736 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。5月1日，她起訴了六名涉及[[弗雷迪·格雷之死|弗雷迪·格雷之死]]的警員{{link-en|謀殺罪 (美國法律)|Murder (United States law)|二級謀殺}}與過失殺人（Involuntary manslaughter）罪<ref name="Calvert-Palazzolo-2015">{{cite news |last1=Calvert |first1=Scott |last2=Palazzolo |first2=Joe |date=April 30, 2015 |title=After Baltimore Riots, Focus Turns to New Prosecutor: City State's Attorney Marilyn Mosby must decide whether to charge police in man's death |work=Wall Street Journal |url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/after-baltimore-riots-focus-turns-to-new-prosecutor-1430356697 |accessdate=May 1, 2015 |archive-date=2020-11-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201118123306/https://www.wsj.com/articles/after-baltimore-riots-focus-turns-to-new-prosecutor-1430356697 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="Walsh-2015">{{cite web |last=Walsh |first=Michael |date=May 1, 2015 |title=Freddie Gray's death ruled a homicide; six Baltimore officers charged |work=Yahoo News |url=http://news.yahoo.com/freddie-gray-sustained-fatal-head-injury-in-back-of-police-van--report-124521845.html |accessdate=May 1, 2015 |archive-date=2021-01-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210118152438/https://news.yahoo.com/freddie-gray-sustained-fatal-head-injury-in-back-of-police-van--report-124521845.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==家庭==
她嫁給了巴爾的摩市議員尼克·莫斯比<ref name="Calvert-Palazzolo-2015"/>，兩人在2005年結婚{{sfn|Adams|2013|p=A10}}。他們育有兩個女兒<ref name= topprosecutor/>，住在鄰近巴爾的摩市的{{link-en|水庫山區 (巴爾的摩)|Reservoir Hill, Baltimore|水庫山區}}<ref>{{cite news |last=Davis |first=Krishana |date=July 3, 2013 |title=Marilyn Mosby Launches Campaign for State's Attorney Post |work=The Baltimore Afro-American |page=A4 |url=http://www.afro.com/marilyn-mosby-launches-campaign-for-states-attorney-post/ |accessdate=2015-05-03 |archive-date=2020-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200812042329/http://www.afro.com/marilyn-mosby-launches-campaign-for-states-attorney-post/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

